Package: refinerGUI
Type: Shiny
Title: Shiny Interface for Indirect Reference Interval Estimation with refineR
Version: 0.1.2
Authors@R: c(
    person("refinerGUI contributors", role = c("aut", "cre"))
    )
Description: Provides a local R Shiny interface for estimating reference
    intervals from real-world data using the refineR package. The application
    supports local CSV and packaged sample data intake, documented refineR
    estimation controls, grouped analysis by sex and age metadata, checkpointed
    grouped runs, reproducible settings import and export, and local result
    review.
License: GPL-3
Encoding: UTF-8
Imports:
    jsonlite,
    later,
    refineR,
    shiny
